Example datasets provided in HiCExperiment & HiContactsData

Usage

data(centros_yeast)

contacts_yeast(full = FALSE)

contacts_yeast_eco1(full = FALSE)

Format

An object of class "GRanges".

Source

HiContacts

Arguments

full

Whether to import all interactions
